Load cbb teams box score stats

load_team_box_scores.Rd

Pull in statistics aggregated by team and game for a given season.

Usage

load_team_box_scores(seasons = most_recent_season())

Arguments

seasons

an integer of seasons to fetch data for. Defaults to the most recent season. Pass in TRUE to fetch all seasons.

Value

a dataframe of team box scores.

Examples

load_team_box_scores()
